title: What?
text: What? I don't get it, I download, open it, it takes me to play store, I open it from play store it takes me back to app, I try and open it again from app which again takes me back to play store which brings me to this review. Annoyed.
Even as an adult I like it
My kids enjoy it and is the best I have seen,
Different games in one app is always a plus.

title: Too slow, phone frozen
text: Too slow, phone frozen Froze the phone! Uninstalled.
replyText:
Thank you for your feedback.
We understand you use Galaxy S III - the app was checked on few different Galaxy S III devices,
and once again after we saw your comment. Unfortunately we couldn't reproduce the problem,
as it worked flawlessly in all of our tests.

We will be happy to assist you further at kidoko+support@kidokoinside.com.
